1. *Kasnim* na sastanak sa šefom. (I am late for the meeting with my boss.)
2. On *kasni* pet minuta. (He is five minutes late.)
3. *Kasnije* ću ti javiti da li mogu da dođem na rođendan. (I will let you know later if I can come to the birthday party.)
4. Doći ću *kasnije*. (I will come later.)
5. Nemoj da mi *kasniš* na dogovorene sastanke. (Don't be late for our scheduled meetings.)
6. On *kasni* svaki put kada mora da ustane rano. (He is always late when he has to wake up early.)
7. *Kasno* je, trebalo bi da idemo kući. (It's late, we should go home.)
8. Molim vas, nemojte *kasniti* na avion. (Please don't be late for the flight.)
9. Danas sam *kasnio* na posao zbog gužve u saobraćaju. (Today I was late for work due to traffic jam.)
10. Sutra ujutru *ne želim kasniti* na važan sastanak. (Tomorrow morning, I don't want to be late for an important meeting.)